features: ​【Lifelike Simulation】This 6 feet faux olive tree is carefully crafted to mimic the appearance of olive tree, looking as close to reality as possible. Single trunk splits into several stems, adorned with dozens of olive fruits, which made of rubber silk fabric. Clearly textured olive leaves and vivid color makes this fake tree a timeless seasonal home decor and will definitely make you feel the existence of nature.

【Free Maintenance】This fake olive tree doesn't need sunlight, and fertilizing and watering it will save you from the trouble of falling leaves. Make sure Artificial Olive Trees are lifelike, evergreen, and require no pruning. No need to water every day or pay special attention, just wipe it off with a damp cloth when it gets dusty. You will love how it brings life to your room without the added maintenance of a live plant

【Vivid Realistic Olive Tree】Featuring lush silvery-green oblong leaves, long slender branches, and dark purple olives.Our faux plants outfitted with sturdy inner metal wires, adjust the branch to the shape you like. This artificial plants indoor will maintain its height, color and shape for years without pruning and shaping to ensure the aesthetic is maintained. Craft your ideal olive tree to decor your home !

【Safe Materials】This artificial tree is made of durable and premium silk material(real touch, waterproof, eco friendly).The black nursery pot is made of hard PP material with cement poured inside which to prevent children,pets knock it down.we suggest to placing it in bigger decorative planter to make the faux tree be more perfect. All materials are flame-retardant treated, TÜV certified, without any odor, so it is no problem even if placed in a sealed environment

【Easy to Assemble】Realead artificial olive trees indoor are easy to install, just loosen the black straps on the trunk and insert the corresponding numbered branches into the trunk. And the main tree trunk come pre-assembled in heavy-duty pots made of plastic and concrete, so each tree can stand on its own. The black nursery pot is 4.5 inch tall and 6 inch width. Recommend you place this tree into a decorative pot, which will enhance the overall decorative effect.

【Perfect Size for Decoration】This 6 foot tall olive tree artificial is is perfectly sized for interior decoration. It is a great ideal decorating for living rooms, bedrooms, study room, dining rooms and offices, and is also perfect for entryways, patios and commercial locations such as bookstores and coffee shops. It's also a great gift for Christmas/Thanksgiving/housewarming, for friends or family. You’ll wish you found this years ago !

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I’ve ordered a couple of artificial trees and I’ve bought a couple of them in stores, set them up at home and did not like them. That is…….until I purchased this olive tree! I love it!!! This tree looks so realistic and I get a lot of compliments. It warmed up my space and when I look over in that corner, I smile. Your home should reflect your personality and what you like, not what is the current trend. I need to live in an environment that is calm and flows in an aesthetically pleasing way. My personality is pretty hyper, so low key natural colors help balance me out. lol This tree really complemented my house and warmed up the chosen space enough without overcrowding. This olive tree is well-made, came in a timely manner and was packaged well. Only one olive fell off when I was unpacking it.. the branches were easy to move around and after I found the right pot it fit perfect in the corner. I feel this purchase was a very good choice on my part.. if you are looking for something to warm up a space in your room and give you some sort of calm and balance in a hectic life, try this Olive tree and you’ll be as surprised I am at how different your home will look. Price point was also very reasonable. Win win!!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Color of main tree and branches
reviews.reviewText: This is my third tree that I have ordered. My first two trees were 6 and 5 ft tall, and they are beautiful. I ordered a third tree in a 4 ft size recently and was very surprised at how different it was from the first two I ordered. I am not sure what has happened, but the stem and branches are painted a light green rather than the light tan color of the first two that I previously ordered. I thought there might be a mistake so I decided to order a replacement wondering if it was a mistake. The fourth tree I received is also painted a light green color on the main tree and branches. I am not sure if this is the case for the bigger trees now, but I would definitely not recommend ordering the 4ft tree. If they change the color back to how it used to be, it would drastically change my review.I contacted the seller and they are fantastic on customer service! They are prompt in their communication, polite and friendly in their correspondence, and go above and beyond for customer satisfaction. They have noted the color change in the 4 feet trees and have said that they would be changing out this batch to go back to the original brown color for the branches. They sent pictures to verify that they have gone through their inventory.These are very beautiful trees, and I wouldn't hesitate at all to purchase from this company. They will keep their word and make sure that you are fully satisfied with your purchase. They also don't erase bad reviews and will seek to make it right. No company can be perfect, but it's encouraging to see a company work toward excellence in their business. Athough I initially gave a one star for the color, I am changing it now to a 5 star because of their customer service. Thanks, Realead! I wish more businesses were like your company.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 10, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This faux olive tree is beautiful! Perfect fullness and the quality is fantastic. I highly recommend it! It is much better than anything I’ve seen in store! I got the 7ft tree and the only downside is the base is too small for the tree and it tips over. I have it in a large pot and have towels and sheets filling in the gaps and a weighted blanket on top of the pot base to keep it standing upright. I understand the small pot base is likely so it can fit in most decorative pot openings but it just doesn’t work for this tall of a tree. It would be 5 stars if not for this issue!

Are real olive trees are easier to duplicate than other species? Have fake tree-making methods dramatically improved? I don't know, but these faux olive trees are great. They're fake but not offensively so.I bought two of them for the west wing at church. I put them in nice-looking ceramic pots and I think that always helps artificial plants look better than they might otherwise. I covered all the support and stuffing with some coarse mulch/tree bark from the garden centre and all told I think everything looks pretty good.
